		<RichText x="738" y="255" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="434" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">掠食型会吞噬6m内最近的基础型，然后进入为期20s的狂暴状态，且体型变大。<br/>狂暴状态会转为不断向玩家攻击。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="424" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#bfdfff">非狂暴：<span color="#ffffff">掠食型朝前咬一口，造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">50%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。<br/></span><span>已狂暴：</span><span color="#ffffff">掠食型不断追着玩家咬，频率高速度快，持续造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">100%.50%,30%,<br/>20%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
