		<RichText x="66" y="912" width="360" height="58" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">核心守塔机制：<br/>掠食型吞噬的基础型计入进度。<br/>击败掠食型推进<span color="#bfffbf">11%</span><span>(220)进度，恢复全队20能量。</span></p>
			</content>
